snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. Next - Factory Stage Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Take a peek at this newly-updated factory stage, featuring bunten's arrangement of "Steam Gardens" from Super Mario Odyssey! ⛰️ 🏭

If you'd like to see more news & updates on Super Mario Bros. Next, join our Discord server, at https://discord.gg/EnESkrr!
